title: Stargate SG1 Season 10 Disk 3 of 5
description:
HERE IT IS FINALLY On the home stretch.
The 10th and final season.
Holy Crap it only took 20 years...
Anyway
NTSC, 16:9 widescreen format in a iso file of the DVD from the box set. Mount it or burn it then watch it or sleep thru it. It is all there with menus ect. This season they include the directors commentary and a few more cheesy bonus features or specials. There are no sub languages or text. Sorry but they got cheap again.

Any problems kindly keep them to yourself or ask someone who can help.
